<br>
Though if you're capable of going to Luclin, I would suggest hunting Sensate Reishi elders in your mid teens to find Fists of Wood (5/20 rare drop h2h weapon) for your monk.  Those will last into early 20s.<br>
<br>
Mid 20s sounds a bit early to take on the goo with the fighting batons... I'm thinking more closer to late 20s or early 30s, though I'll have to check on that.<br>
<br>
